{"tid":989161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接二連三搞失蹤 日本政府拒絕中國強送實習生入境","createTime":"2019-01-20T15:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T16:17:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0cec6e33973e83af71a8b5e3d859266760781ccb","tid":989161,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTPQX0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTPQX0F.jpg&h=5e461509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國實習生在日本企業學習，卻接二連三搞失蹤。圖為中國遊客在日本東京街道情形。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-20 18:39<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國籍實習生入境日本後竟接二連三奇異失蹤，日本政府有鑑於此，本月15日拒絕10名中籍實習生入境，這一行人17日隨即被日方遣返回中國，日方抨擊，事前已告知中國政府，不懂中方為何執意送人過來。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本《共同社》報導，這10名中國籍實習生15日搭機抵達愛知縣常滑市中部國際機場，當場被海關拒絕入境，負責接洽的日方監理團體指出，雖與中方有簽訂合約，替實習生媒介有人力需求的日本企業，但中國實習生報到後常接二連三失蹤，讓這些企業相當頭大。<br />\n<br />\n監理團體理事長河守俊行提到，在2018年12月就發函告知中方終止合約內容，詢問這10名實習生，他們卻都說不知道此事，但還是必須讓他們回中國，因此在入境管理收容處睡了2晚就直接遣返；他抨擊中方「明明已經通告了，但中國方面還單方面地送人過來」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2677734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2677734&d=EwNonSrI7SgiT3FBTNcE3r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b164c0a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2677734&h=e331a143\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2677734</a>"},{"pid":"6fe257dff71eb678ae7fccf42f8b71350aec4d95","tid":989161,"uid":70786,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"支那人都係間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4af1a9c63cb2fb1d7c056f60a092b21c024e1fc","tid":989161,"uid":145769,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:45:37.000Z","msg":"港澳無得講<br />\n唔明點解其他國家會接收中國移民<br />\n<br />\n多人，唔合群，唔會理會移民國語言或傳統，盡攞福利"},{"pid":"02997669e8ac792340b4c5dcf93b7f4710855dd7","tid":989161,"uid":81424,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"//<em>接二連三搞失蹤</em>//<br />\n<br />\n寫做「接二連三失踨」唔得咩?<br />\n呢家D中文報紙係都要搞搞下 唔似共匪中文唔心息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f8853eaa244b57c66f10abb45eae579be7596a","tid":989161,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"喱返357年就拎護照轉生"},{"pid":"86c2aa76b4c1c7f5b4678e1332be167d3624be92","tid":989161,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"基本所有去外國讀書既支那人都係間諜"},{"pid":"4b24d6a690230d00cea37427f2633e2f4ac2a9a5","tid":989161,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18d537221937351d2f6715eb563c48931cee6bcf","tid":989161,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"入咗共青團受訓過先出得去，㗎仔唔係咁都唔知嘛？"},{"pid":"f1b22a01e5c6d64b785d3c1100c8125cfbe6dcf8","tid":989161,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"請世界繼續杯葛支那"}]}